Interface IceSoapListParser<ReturnType>

  • Type Parameters:
    ReturnType - The type to return.
    All Superinterfaces:
    IceSoapParser<List<ReturnType>>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IceSoapListParserImpl

    public interface IceSoapListParser<ReturnType>
extends IceSoapParser<List<ReturnType>>
    Extension of IceSoapParser that allows the ability to register special observers that will be called every time a new item is passed.
    Author:
    Alex Gilleran

      void registerItemObserver(ItemObserver<ReturnType> observer)
      Registers an observer with the parser - any object passed to this method will have its ItemObserver.onNewItem(Object) method called every time a new object is parsed.
